name: Happy Yak Ranchero Soup
description: Inspired by the big flavours of the American southwest, Rachero soup delivers bold spices with hearty lentils and soy protein in a bright tomato broth.Ingredients: tomato broth (dehydrated vegetables (tomato, onions), corn maltodextrin, glucose solids, hydrolyzed corn protein, modified corn starch, potato starch, sugar, salt, caramel (sulphites), spices, yeast extract, corn fiber, garlic and onion powder; citric acid, artificial flavour), red lentils, rice, dehydrated soy proteins chunks (textured soy proteins, corn semolina, oat flakes (gluten), wheal flour, onion flakes, spices]. dehydrated vegetables (carrot, potato, onion, celery, leek, red and green tell peppers).May contain: nuts, peanuts, sesame, milk, egg, seafood, soy, wheat and mustard.
